snippet.title: You probably HAVEN'T LAUGHED THAT HARD BEFORE! - Funny ANIMALS vs HUMAN TECHNOLOGY
snippet.description:
Funny animals are the best entertainment ever! They make us laugh all the time and never fail to cheer us up! Funny animal videos are simply the best! This animal compilation is super hard try not to laugh challenge! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, parrots, toad, lizards, guinea pig... use phones and computers, watch tv, react to technology,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
